                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we will learn how to wrap up a client meeting.\nEnding a meeting well is very important in the workplace.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/e3bfc0c0-20ba-45d6-a7e7-59938a4a61f9-client-meeting---3-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "When you finish a discussion, you should confirm the decision.\nSay: \"So we've agreed on [decision]. Next, I'll [action].\"\nExample: \"So we've agreed on the new timeline. Next, I'll send the updated plan.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/e3bfc0c0-20ba-45d6-a7e7-59938a4a61f9-client-meeting---3-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Makes sense!",
                    "text": "You should also tell the client when you will share something.\nSay: \"I'll share [item] by [day]. We can talk again on [day].\"\nExample: \"I'll share the cost details by Wednesday. We can talk again on Friday.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/e3bfc0c0-20ba-45d6-a7e7-59938a4a61f9-client-meeting---3-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Okay!",
                    "text": "Before ending, always check if the client has more questions.\nAsk: \"Anything else before our next meeting?\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/e3bfc0c0-20ba-45d6-a7e7-59938a4a61f9-client-meeting---3-(1).jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
